    "Figure 1 -Experimental Setup.",
    "A displays the information extraction pipeline.",
    "The psychiatry reports (n=100) were transferred to a csv table.",
    "Our pipeline then iterates over all reports with the predefined prompt and outputs a JavaScript Object Notation-File (JSON) file with all Large Language Model (LLM) outputs (PRED).",
    "The relevant classes (suicidality present: yes or no) were then extracted from the LLM output, which was more verbose in some cases."
